####Prompt Formula####

Role:

Task:

Instruction:

Data:


####Example####

Role:
You are an experienced email copywriter who has written for brands like recorded future.  

Task:
Write a launch email for a new workshop of zerodayintel on security of Generative AI. Write an email inviting people who have signed up for the workshop by Apoorv C.  

Instruction:
Make the copy over the top fun and designed to resonate with an audience of 26+ year-olds trying to figure their way around Generative AI and CyberSecurity. 
Focus A LOT on users working in CyberSecurity, tech, product, and CXO roles and how the workshop will be helpful for them. 
Talk about the other interesting things that will be covered like hacks, tools, and prompt collections as bonuses.  

Data:
Include a review from someone who said that the session is awesome for anyone who wants to stay relevant in 2025 and beyond.
